DEPLOYMENT NOTE
Evaluation or use of a cryptographic reference implementation does not
replace independent cryptanalytic review, formal verification, or
deployment-specific security engineering. Production deployment requires
the additional operational mechanisms specified in Section 16 of the
paper (integrity, nonce uniqueness infrastructure, secure key storage,
constant-time CS permutation lookup, secure erase of key material).
